Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.91,0:01:36.93,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The Macross, which launched in haste\Nin order to avoid an enemy attack,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:40.44,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}failed in its attempt to execute a space fold\Nto the far side of the Moon.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:44.37,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Instead, the Macross and its island base\Nwere transported not to the Moon,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:47.09,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}but just inside the orbit of Pluto.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:49.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}Daedulus, respond!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:53.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}Air leaks at each block confirmed!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:56.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}Service personnel, please stand by!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:49.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Bringing in the shelters is our first priority.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:52.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That's where the evacuees from the city are!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:59.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Captain, we can't contact the\NPrometheus or the Daedalus.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:00.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The chances of finding any survivors are...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.36,0:02:04.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I thought as much.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:06.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}They're just aircraft carriers.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:09.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}They weren't designed to\Nfly into space.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.72,0:02:13.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hayase, issue an order\Nto the work vessels.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:15.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Tell them to pull the carriers here toward us.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:20.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Don't tell me you're going to dock with\Nthem instead of ARMD-I and ARMD-II!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:24.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We should be able to use their\Nship-based weapons.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:25.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I wonder if it will work?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'm counting on the efforts of the work teams.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:32.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Once we've retrieved the people\Nfrom the shelters,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:35.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}we're going to round up everything\Nthat's floating around out there.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:38.15,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hikaru Ichijo, the air-race pilot who came to see{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:41.21,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}the launching of the Macross only to\Nfind himself in the middle of a war,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:44.03,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}and Lynn Minmay, the young girl\Nthat he rescued,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:47.53,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}narrowly escaped death by flying\ninside the Macross itself.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:48.80,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}However...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:52.28,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FF00&\pos(82,134)}LYNN MINMAY{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:50.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Here goes.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:00.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Come on, why don't you\Ngive up on that?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:04.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It will be faster just to call someone\Nto come get us, right?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What is it?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:16.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The communicator's busted.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:23.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What's that?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:24.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A compass.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:28.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I thought a compass was shaped like this.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}So, it's not the kind of compass\Nyou draw circles with.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:42.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This ship is huge.\NWith this, we'll always know where the racer is.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:47.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}There's nothing but pipes everywhere!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:49.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I wonder, if it's because we're\Nnear the energy block?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:51.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hot!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:55.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'm fine. See?\NIt was just a little hot, that's all.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:56.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You'll get hurt if you're not careful.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:57.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Okay.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hey, be careful!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:10.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Fourth time's not a charm either, huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:12.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Are you sure we're not going the wrong way?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:15.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We should be heading toward\Nthe bridge, but...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This is the right way. It has to be.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:19.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Let's go?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:20.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:27.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You want us to look for a civilian?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yeah, his name's Hikaru Ichijo, remember?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:31.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}He's like my little brother.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:35.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Now, look here!\NThere's a time and place for jokes, and...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:35.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Claudia...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:42.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Major Focker, this is Captain Global.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:44.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I think you're already aware{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:48.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}that there are currently over 50,000 civilians\Ntaking shelter aboard this ship.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:51.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If the enemy were to launch a surprise\Nattack, there's no telling...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}Understood, sir!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:56.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}The lives of 50,000 people are more important\Nthan the life of just one, right?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:58.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well, you see...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:03.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Blockhead...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:10.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hey, does it look brighter over there to you?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You're right!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We did it!\N{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}We did it!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It looks like we can climb up over there!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:50.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}An airlock for the giants, huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What's wrong?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:12.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What on earth is going on?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Maybe, we're having a bad dream.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:18.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The captain is currently inspecting the ship.\NOver.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:19.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I made some coffee.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:30.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I swear, and all because the Captain\Nhad to execute a space fold.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:33.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Not only can our ship not make\Ncontact with the Earth,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:35.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}now we have these 50,000 civilian refugees.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:37.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If we're attacked out here, we're done for.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:42.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But, even without fold communication, given\Nenough time, normal radio waves should...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:46.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Right, we could still make contact\Nwith UN High Command.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:50.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But that would reveal our\nlocation to the enemy.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:51.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Oh...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:57.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}1st Lt. Hayase, block RX-24 is requesting\Ndirections to an evacuation center.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We don't even have time for a cup of coffee.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:05.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}How's your leg?\NDoes it still hurt?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:09.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}My leg's fine, but I'm really thirsty.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:10.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Water, huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:14.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If it was food, there's a little\Nback at the racer, but...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:22.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You may be able to drink some water after all!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:23.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hang on a second!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:34.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Ready, okay!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:08.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It tastes great!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:10.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And it feels great!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:13.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hey!\NI think I'll take a shower!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:14.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:17.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Right now?\NHere?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:20.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yup, I'm all covered in sweat.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:30.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well, I guess it'd be better\Nif I go over there, huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:33.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Thank you for being so considerate.\NYou've made me happy.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:39.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Also, if you could set up a screen\Nover there, I'd appreciate it.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:40.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Aye, aye.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:45.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Is this okay?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:46.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Thanks!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:52.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What is it, Minmay?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:56.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:08:59.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Really...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:03.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Jeez...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:15.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Maybe I teased him a little too much.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sorry, Hikaru!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:22.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hikaru, what is it?\NAre you mad?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hikaru!\NAnswer me!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:29.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I found my work clothes.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:31.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You can wear them if you like.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:36.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I feel so much better!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:38.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Why don't you take a shower, too?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sure, I was gonna.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:45.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This shirt is so baggy!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:49.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I found some canned food too.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:50.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You want some?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:52.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Terrific!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Man, I sure am hungry.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:57.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yum!\NThis is great!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:01.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hey, are you sure you should\Neat that all at once?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:03.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}No problem!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:05.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We'll find the exit tomorrow.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:07.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And, if we don't?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:09.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This ship's only about a kilometer long at most.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I think we'll be fine.{\b0}
