Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:21.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I've lost my appetite.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:22.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Beaten already, huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:23.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Who is?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:32.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If you think about it, it's only been one day.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:36.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yeah, I got a call from my Sempai and\NI came out to see the Macross.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:39.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The next thing I know, not only am\NI being attacked by aliens,...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:41.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}but I wind up in space inside the ship.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I wonder how my aunt and uncle are doing?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If they made it to the shelter,\NI think they'll be fine.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:51.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yeah, the soldiers will protect them.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:55.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The soldiers, huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:03.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hey, that's not such a good idea!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:07.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If you fall asleep in a place like\Nthis, you'll catch a cold.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:14.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Oh, so that's the kind of person you are.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:16.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I had no idea!\NUnbelievable!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hey, wait a minute!\NIt was a rat!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:23.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Rats!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:24.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What did I tell you?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:27.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's a ship, so they made this their home\Nlong before us humans.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I can't stand rats!\NHurry up and make them go away!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:34.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hey, I wonder if that's their nest?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Oh, no!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:38.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'll explain the situation to them tomorrow\Nand get them to share the bed with you.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:10.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Now, if we're here, then...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:13.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hey!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:17.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This shows that this is our second\Nday as castaways.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:21.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Good idea, huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:23.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Uh, sure.\NWell, I'll be back later.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:25.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}See you!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:28.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}How could she do that to my precious racer?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:29.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Jeez...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:36.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Ow!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:39.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Ow!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:44.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}How'd it go?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:49.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That sure smells good!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:52.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Our food will last longer this way.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:55.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Just what you'd expect from a girl whose\Nfamily runs a Chinese restaurant!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}No way!\NThat's my aunt's place.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:00.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I just go there to visit sometimes.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:02.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Where's your family then?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yokohama...\NWe have a restaurant in Chinatown.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:06.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Here!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:09.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Oh, I'd just assumed that your\Nfamily ran a Chinese restaurant...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:10.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Huh?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:20.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Today's our third day, huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Mom...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:40.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Welcome back!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:46.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I give up.\NIt's like we're on some desert island in a far-off sea.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:47.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Oh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:49.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But, this is the last of our supplies.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:53.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Why don't I go outside and call for help?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:54.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Outside?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:58.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'll go out into space through the airlock,\Nthen back onto the ship through another one.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:00.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But, you don't have a spacesuit!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:05.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}They use this helmet in combat,\Nso it's pretty airtight.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:07.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If we reinforce it, I think we\Ncan make this work.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:08.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:14.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}With it and this pilot suit, I should\Nbe able to last for a while.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:16.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:19.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Do you understand how to work the switch now?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:20.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yes...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:24.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But, what will you do for air?\NYou don't even have an oxygen tank.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:26.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I think I can hold out for two or three minutes.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:28.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You're going to hold your breath?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:30.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's no different from diving in the ocean, right?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.21,0:14:34.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Where are you going?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:38.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}To check the direction of the nearest\Nairlock from the window.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:43.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Again? You can't get spooked by\Nevery little thing that floats by, okay?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:51.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Is that a tuna?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:53.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A tuna?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:54.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A tuna!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:00.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Tuna!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:03.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sashimi!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hang in there!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:09.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Are you all right?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:14.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I did it!\NWe won't be worrying about food for a...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:23.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You shouldn't be so disappointed.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:26.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Not many people have ever\Ncaught a tuna in space.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:29.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But, now I can't go back out there again.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:34.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}When I was pinned under the tuna,\Nmy suit got snagged on its teeth.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:39.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Our plan of going outside the ship to\Nget help just went up in smoke.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:41.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hey, how about opening a hole\Nin the ceiling and going up?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:43.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I thought of that, too...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:46.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But, where are we gonna get tools\Nto cut through steel plates?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What about blasting through?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:53.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We've just about used up the\Nrest of the racer's fuel.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:54.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}On what?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:55.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:07.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Thanks.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:12.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}So I told him, it doesn't matter how\Nmany fighter planes you have,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:14.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}without pilots, what are ya gonna do?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:18.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Good work.\NSo, how are the refugees holding up?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:22.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I hear they've calmed down a bit and have\Nstarted building a refugee camp.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:24.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A refugee camp?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:35.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}...since then, Sempai always hits on girls by taking\Nthem up and doing dive bombing runs!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:36.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Really?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:58.06,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\i1}When the midnight bell tolled,\Nthe magic spell wore off.{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:05.08,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\i1}Down the staircase she rushed,\Nas if trying to outrun it.{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:12.07,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\i1}And at the top of the stairs,\Na single glass slipper...{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:15.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You've got a nice voice.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:20.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You may not believe it, but I took singing\Nlessons in middle school.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:25.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And dancing...\Nand acting lessons too!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:27.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You sure have done a lot.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:29.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I've just flown planes my whole life.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:31.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Oh, but that's great!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:33.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Putting everything you've got\Ninto just one thing.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:35.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You think so?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:38.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}So what do you want to be?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:40.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Me? Oh...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:43.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A bride, I guess.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:45.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A bride?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:48.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I see.\NWell, I bet you'll make a great one.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:50.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Thanks...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:53.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But, it's all over for us anyway.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:56.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hey, that's not true!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:58.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}My Sempai and the others will find us.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:00.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's been twelve days now.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:04.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}They'll have given us up for dead.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:05.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Even my aunt and uncle...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.98,0:19:22.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We'll make a good dinner for\Nthe rats when we die, huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:25.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Just like that tuna did.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:28.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Don't say things like that.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:29.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's okay.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But I just...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:36.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I wish I could have worn a wedding dress\Njust once before I died.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:40.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Minmay...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:49.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What do you say we have a wedding ceremony?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You're right.\NThat'd be great!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:08.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I... Are you sure you're okay\Nwith someone like me?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:14.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Say, Hikaru...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:18.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If we're going to die anyway,\Nlet's get it over with...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:20.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}and throw ourselves out into space!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:23.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Where did that come from?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:25.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Let's die together!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:29.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Don't be stupid!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:31.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You fell from the sky and\Ndrifted in space, but you're still alive!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:35.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You'll be saved this time too! I promise!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:38.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sure, you say that, but...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:40.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We can't find a single way out of here!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:43.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You're just scared to die!\NCoward!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I guess I am kinda pathetic.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:56.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'm just a guy who only knows\Nhow to fly planes, but...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:58.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But, I...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:00.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You make me...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:01.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'm sorry.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:02.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I didn't mean it like that.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:05.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I guess I got a little crazy for a second.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:07.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:11.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:36.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}An enemy missile!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:37.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's a dud!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.61,0:21:39.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We've gotta get rid of it quick!\NIt's dangerous!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:43.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hey, isn't that Minmay?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:45.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Mr. Mayor!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.53,0:21:56.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}They say they found some people!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:57.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Huh?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.24,0:21:58.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A boy and a girl!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.47,0:21:59.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You've gotta be kiddin' me!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:01.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hey, you're right!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:05.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}How?!\NWe're inside a spaceship, but...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:08.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Wow! Amazing!\NThe restaurant and Yot-chan's house are just like they were!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:11.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hey!\NMinmay!{\b0}
